sexpression.lexer

Class WhitespaceState

  • java.lang.Object
    • sexpression.lexer.WhitespaceState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILexerState

    public class WhitespaceState
extends java.lang.Object
implements ILexerState
    State Design Pattern

    When the lexer is in this state, is in the middle of reading whitespace (not in the middle of reading a word).
